      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·陳風·004.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">東門之池.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>東門之池，可以漚麻。彼美淑姬，可與晤歌。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The moat at the east gate
Is fit to steep hemp in.
That beautiful, virtuous, lady
Can respond to you in songs.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
